1
00:00:06,218 --> 00:00:10,507
We celebrate the Govardhan Puja and Gopuja -

2
00:00:10,507 --> 00:00:12,633
the Worship of the Cows.

3
00:00:16,676 --> 00:00:18,692
We know, on Srila Gurudev’s veranda...

4
00:00:18,692 --> 00:00:19,819
He is sitting there.

5
00:00:19,819 --> 00:00:23,322
If anyone will walk in before him

6
00:00:23,322 --> 00:00:25,541
with a bag or something

7
00:00:25,541 --> 00:00:27,232
whatever it might be,

8
00:00:27,232 --> 00:00:30,890
he has to know what's inside it.

9
00:00:30,890 --> 00:00:33,261
You cannot just walk by him...

10
00:00:33,261 --> 00:00:37,435
He'll stare... You know...

11
00:00:37,435 --> 00:00:40,342
He'll wanna know!

12
00:00:40,342 --> 00:00:44,157
So, those who are his permanent servitors,

13
00:00:44,157 --> 00:00:47,967
his veranda servitors like Bhakti Lalita,

14
00:00:47,967 --> 00:00:52,340
she would just show him all of her stuff

15
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:54,635
without him asking,

16
00:00:54,635 --> 00:00:57,353
knowing that he wanted to see it.

17
00:00:57,353 --> 00:01:00,675
So, one of the things that,

18
00:01:00,675 --> 00:01:03,421
there is a refrigerator

19
00:01:03,421 --> 00:01:05,923
that she used and some others.

20
00:01:05,923 --> 00:01:08,827
So, she would get the... her,

21
00:01:11,671 --> 00:01:14,110
how do you say it, the...

22
00:01:14,110 --> 00:01:16,153
say, whatever she was eating for that day,

23
00:01:16,153 --> 00:01:19,735
and have to walk in front of Gurudev.

24
00:01:19,735 --> 00:01:24,722
So, she would just turn and show him,

25
00:01:24,722 --> 00:01:28,115
like just present it to him and he'd look.

26
00:01:28,131 --> 00:01:31,653
Especially he had some interest in,

27
00:01:31,653 --> 00:01:36,116
extraordinary interest in different types of food. 

28
00:01:36,116 --> 00:01:38,375
So, she showed him one day

29
00:01:38,375 --> 00:01:39,811
and there is like different types of

30
00:01:39,811 --> 00:01:44,046
lettuce, and celery, and green things and like that...

31
00:01:44,046 --> 00:01:48,994
And Gurudev looked down like this and he said:

32
00:01:48,994 --> 00:01:53,103
“I can see that your Lord is Krishna”,

33
00:01:53,103 --> 00:01:55,923
like that, and then just...

34
00:01:55,923 --> 00:01:57,983
And she looked at me like...

35
00:01:57,983 --> 00:02:00,013
"What's that?"

36
00:02:00,013 --> 00:02:04,161
He said: “I can see your Lord is Krishna”.

37
00:02:04,161 --> 00:02:08,713
And he looked to me to see if I caught what he said.

38
00:02:08,713 --> 00:02:12,838
And then I started smiling and laughing...

39
00:02:12,838 --> 00:02:16,696
And what he meant was, who is Krishna?

40
00:02:16,696 --> 00:02:18,991
We just celebrated Govardhan Puja,

41
00:02:18,991 --> 00:02:24,815
Gava Indra, Govinda - the Lord of the Cows.

42
00:02:24,815 --> 00:02:26,294
So, he is saying:

43
00:02:26,294 --> 00:02:28,548
”When I look at what you are about to eat,

44
00:02:28,548 --> 00:02:32,499
it looks like cow food to me”.

45
00:02:32,499 --> 00:02:36,670
But to say that, that would be insulting...

46
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:37,908
So what did he say?

47
00:02:37,908 --> 00:02:41,218
“I can see that your Lord is Krishna”.

